In the MATTER OF the ESTATE OF Yoram KOBY, deceased. (Limor Elbaz and Paul E. Paray, Esquire - Petitioners) C-42 September Term 2018
081136 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001690-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
